<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #222;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  @page { margin: 34mm 0 30mm 0; size: A4; }

  /* ── Fixed header — every page ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .doc-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: -34mm;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 34mm;
    padding: 8mm 20mm 6mm;
    background: #fff;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .firma-info .firma-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  .firma-info .firma-sub  { font-size: 9.5px; color: #555; margin-top: 2px; }
  .logo { max-height: 52px; max-width: 140px; object-fit: contain; }

  .header-rule {
    position: fixed;
    top: -2mm;
    left: 20mm; right: 20mm;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1.5px solid #333;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Fixed footer — every page ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .doc-footer {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: -30mm;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 30mm;
    padding: 3mm 20mm 6mm;
    border-top: 0.5px solid #ccc;
    font-size: 8.5px;
    color: #555;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .doc-footer > div { flex: 1; line-height: 1.65; }
  .footer-section-label { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1px; }

  /* ── Main content ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .content { padding: 0 20mm; }

  .empf-block { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .empf-absender { font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .doc-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .doc-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; }
  .doc-subtitle { font-size: 13px; color: #555; margin-top: 3px; }

  .meta-table { font-size: 11px; border-collapse: collapse; }
  .meta-table td { padding: 2px 0; }
  .meta-table td:first-child { color: #555; }
  .meta-table td:last-child { padding-left: 12px; }

  /* Positionen */
  table.pos {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
  }
  table.pos thead { display: table-header-group; }
  table.pos th {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #ccc;
    border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
  }
  table.pos th:last-child, table.pos td:last-child { border-right: none; }
  table.pos th.rechts, table.pos td.rechts { text-align: right; }
  table.pos td {
    padding: 5px 8px;
    vertical-align: top;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    border-right: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  table.pos tbody tr { page-break-inside: avoid; }

  /* Totals */
  .totals {
    margin-left: auto;
    width: 260px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .totals td { padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px; }
  .totals .brutto td {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-top: 1.5px solid #333;
  }

  .zusatz-block {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #444;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-top: 8px;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  .closing {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
    margin-bottom: 8mm;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

{{> header}}

<div class="content">

  <div class="empf-block">
    <div class="empf-absender">{{firma.firma}} · {{firma.strasse}} · {{firma.ort}}</div>
    <div style="font-weight:bold">{{angebot.empf}}</div>
    {{#if angebot.str}}<div>{{angebot.str}}</div>{{/if}}
    {{#if angebot.ort}}<div>{{angebot.ort}}</div>{{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="doc-meta">
    <div>
      <div class="doc-title">Angebot</div>
      {{#if angebot.titel}}<div class="doc-subtitle">{{angebot.titel}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>
    <table class="meta-table">
      <tr><td>Angebots-Nr.:</td><td><strong>{{angebot.nr}}</strong></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Datum:</td><td>{{angebot.datumFormatiert}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Gültig bis:</td><td>{{angebot.gueltigBisFormatiert}}</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <table class="pos">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:32px">Pos.</th>
        <th style="width:70px">Stunden</th>
        <th>Bezeichnung</th>
        <th class="rechts" style="width:110px">Einzelpreis</th>
        <th class="rechts" style="width:110px">Gesamtpreis</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each angebot.positionen}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{posNr @index}}</td>
        <td>{{#if stunden}}{{stunden}}{{else}}–{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{{bezHtml bez}}}</td>
        <td class="rechts">{{#if einzelpreis}}{{fmtEur einzelpreis}}{{else}}Pauschal{{/if}}</td>
        <td class="rechts">{{fmtEur gesamtpreis}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <table class="totals">
    <tr><td>Nettobetrag:</td><td style="text-align:right">{{angebot.nettoFormatiert}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>MwSt. {{angebot.mwstLabel}}:</td><td style="text-align:right">{{angebot.ustFormatiert}}</td></tr>
    <tr class="brutto"><td><strong>Gesamtbetrag:</strong></td><td style="text-align:right"><strong>{{angebot.bruttoFormatiert}}</strong></td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="closing">
    <p>Dieses Angebot ist <strong>30 Tage</strong> gültig. Bei Fragen stehen wir Ihnen gerne zur Verfügung.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:6px">Wir würden uns sehr freuen, wenn unser Angebot Ihre Zustimmung findet.</p>
  </div>

  {{#if angebot.zusatz}}
  <div class="zusatz-block">
    <strong>Zusätzliche Vereinbarungen:</strong><br>
    {{{angebot.zusatzHtml}}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}

</div>

{{> footer}}

</body>
</html>
